#: 6fb84db2af0c4f65bd0ba9985ab3f806
msgid ""
"The model fitting agrees with the Maximum Likelihood estimates described "
"in the original paper. In addition, MCMC sampling, gives us useful "
"information about the uncertainty of the fits."
